{%- comment -%}
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
SEARCH BLOCKED LIST
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Outputs a normalized, comma-wrapped string of blocked URL paths from the global theme setting
`search_blocked_handles`. Designed to be captured by callers and used with `contains` checks.

Usage:
  {%- capture blocked_search_list -%}{%- render 'search-blocked-list' -%}{%- endcapture -%}
  {%- assign url_path = resource.url | remove_first: '/' | downcase -%}
  {%- assign url_check = ',' | append: url_path | append: ',' -%}
  {%- if blocked_search_list contains url_check -%}{%- continue -%}{%- endif -%}

Output shape (no whitespace, no leading slashes, lowercased):
  ,pages/rsvp,collections/adidas,products/sample,
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign raw = settings.search_blocked_handles | default: '' | strip -%}
{%- if raw == '' -%},{%- else -%}
  {%- assign cleaned = raw | newline_to_br | replace: '<br />', ',' | replace: '<br/>', ',' | replace: '<br>', ',' | replace: ' ', '' | replace: '	', '' | downcase -%}
  {%- assign parts = cleaned | split: ',' -%},{%- for p in parts -%}{%- assign trimmed = p | strip | remove_first: '/' -%}{%- if trimmed != '' -%}{{ trimmed }},{%- endif -%}{%- endfor -%}
{%- endif -%}
